FBIS4-16456 "drsov074_b_94023" FBIS-SOV-94-074 Daily Report 18 Apr 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Military & Nuclear Issues Border Guards Chief Appointed Security Council Member Border Guards Chief Appointed Security Council Member LD1804104194 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1015 GMT 18 Apr 94 LD1804104194 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [Text] Moscow April 18 ITAR-TASS -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin confirmed by decree the appointment of Aleksandr Nikolayev, the commander-in-chief of the border troops of the Russian Federation, a member of the National Security Council of the Russian Federation. This was announced by the presidential press service.
